abstract: DEATH OF HON. DANIEL CADY. Hon. DANIEL CADY died on the 31st October, at his residence in Johnstown, N. Y., aged 88. abstract: THE GALE ON FRIDAY NIGHT.--The gale of Friday night last was the severest experienced at Buffalo in several years. A great deal of injury was done to bridges, piers, shipping and buildings.
